We would like to use Wiki markup functionality and basic editing (style, bold, italic, font-color etc.) for the descriptions of Portfolio entries, just as available for the ticket descriptions in JIRA.

Please add the markup functionality (compare for https://jira.atlassian.com/secure/WikiRendererHelpAction.jspa?section=texteffects) as well as the editing functionality for the form field "description".

