When specifying an estimate for a stage it would be useful if the tool calculated out the other stages using the specified % and then roll up the total estimate, currently if I specify 2 days for implementation the total is 2 days. e.g. we sometimes only estimate the implementation stage and calculate the other stages before rolling up to a total estimate.

