  {panel}

Updates of estimates in JIRA should flow back into Portfolio and update its estimate whilst keeping the original estimate as the “Originally Planned”.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Portfolio Cloud*. Using *JIRA Portfolio Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JPOSERVER-217].
  {panel}

During update plan: would be great to have a checkbox to only show the changed ones.

