when importing existing JIRA issues, it is possible to define the name of a new default parent epic. 
It should be possible to select an existing epic here, and assign all issues to it in bulk (if not selecting anything else for an individual record)

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Portfolio Cloud*. Using *JIRA Portfolio Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JPOSERVER-24].
  {panel}

Please implement a synch between the estimation in JIRA Portfolio and the JIRA Issue. It allready works from JIRA to JIRA Portfolio, but not the other way around.

